<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٨١:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: {قُلْ أَعُوذُ بِرَبِّ الْفَلَقِ <span class="c2">(١)</span> مِنْ شَرِّ مَا خَلَقَ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> وَمِنْ شَرِّ غَاسِقٍ إِذَا وَقَبَ <span class="c2">(٣)</span> وَمِنْ شَرِّ النَّفَّاثَاتِ فِي الْعُقَدِ <span class="c2">(٤)</span>} <span class="c4">[الفلق: ١ - ٤]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ مُجَاهِدٌ:</span> <span class="c1">" الفَلَقُ: الصُّبْحُ،<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">يُقَالُ:</span> أَبْيَنُ مِنْ فَرَقِ وَفَلَقِ الصُّبْحِ،<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ مُجَاهِدٌ:</span> <span class="c3">{غَاسِقٍ}</span>: اللَّيْلُ،<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c3">{إِذَا وَقَبَ}</span>: غُرُوبُ الشَّمْسِ،<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">ويُقَالُ:</span> <span class="c3">{وَقَبَ}</span>: إِذَا دَخَلَ فِي كُلِّ شَيْءٍ وَأَظْلَمَ "<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>-<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٧ص١٣٦:</span> النَّفَّاثَاتُ: السَّوَاحِرُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>